name: Pre-order Superafrican Comicbook
description:
Pre-Order the FIRST EDITION and COLLECTIBLE  Superafrican comicbook about Africa's newest superhero.  Orders will be shipped  February 2014.

All net proceeds from the sale of the comic book will go to onemama.org, a non-profit organization that provides a self-sustaining medical clinic that promotes safe birthing environments; family and financial planning; and trade, craft and agricultural education in Kirindi, Uganda. name: Black President Download
description:
Winner of the 2010 NAACP Image Award for "outstanding World Music Album".

Reviews:

On "Chrome," Sila turns in his most intriguing vocal performance, as his high-pitched screams ("I'm freaking OUT!") complement and punctuate the cool, hepcat flow of the melody. Think of the well-constructed yet laid-back neo-soul of rock quintet Townhall, with James Brown and Prince trading improvisations over the top."-Jambase

"The best of all possible worlds in World Music terms: uptempo, polyrhythmic, socially conscious (but not pedantic), strikingly melodic, and eminently danceable." - San Francisco Bay Guardian

TRACK LISTING
1. Shelter 
2. Beauty Queen

4. Chrome
5. Thief In The House
6. Live It Up
7. You Love You
8. Black President
9. What Makes You Laugh Makes You Cry
10. Kamakosa
11. I'm So Tired
